                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Thames-policeman</hi>, 47.) I found Walker on a beam in the hold, without his shoes—which were in a barge by the vessel—I searched him, and found some things of his own—I found a lot of things strewed about the cabin.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Walker. Q.</hi> How long was it after Johnson was taken? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About ten minutes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Johnson's Defence.</hi> A man in blue asked me if I wanted a job, and took me on board; I was not on my knees at the chest, I was standing up</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Walker's Defence.</hi> I was sleeping in the barge; it rained, and I went into the ship's hold.</p>
